.TP
\fB\-V\fR <col>
vertex color (default: gold)
.TP
\fB\-E\fR <col>
edge color   (default: lightgray)
.HP
\fB\-f\fR <mthd> mthd is face coloring method using color in map (default: n)
.IP
key word: none \- sets no color
n \- by number of sides
